      If Start=1
        Repeat
        Until Inkey$<>"" Or Mousek<>0
      Endif
      Cls
    Else
      Print Fn Zen$(Text$)
    Endif
    Read Text$
    Start=1
  Wend
  Repeat
  Until Inkey$<>"" Or Mousek<>0
  Info:
